dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.enterprise.wf.wres.WorkforceEmployeePoolAssignment
dataStructure.description:
Represents an association class and defines specific characteristics for the assignment of an employee to a pool. For example, assignment of fiber technicians to the Installation and Repair team pools, serving the New York Area in the first quarter.

This entity is optional
